description: Oink and Moo’s goal is to deliver mouth-watering BBQ to New Jersey patrons in a fun, friendly atmosphere. Our meats are smoked low and slow over distinctive hickory, cherry and apple woods right on the truck in a Cookshack commercial-grade smoker.  We serve each meat in a unique style that complements its flavors and makes our food truck not only stand out among food trucks but also as a premier BBQ joint.
name: Oink and Moo BBQ
